Shishi extra/README -- Notes for the extra/ subdirectory.
Copyright (C) 2002, 2003 Simon Josefsson
See the end for copying conditions.

The pam_shishi/ sub-directory contains a PAM module that uses Shishi
for authenticating users.

The inetutils.diff file contains a patch for GNU InetUtils to add
Kerberos 5 authentication support for telnet client and telnetd server
using Shishi.  Apply the patch and build InetUtils using
--enable-encryption --enable-authentication --with-shishi.

The mailutils.diff file contains a patch for GNU MailUtils to add
Kerberos 5 authentication support for the IMAP server using GSS and
Shishi.  Apply the patch, install GSS, and build MailUtils using
--with-gssapi.

